<p>收到客户新提货预约，详情如下：</p>

<p>
收货人信息:<%= @exchange.fullname %>,&nbsp;&nbsp;
<%= @exchange.phone %>&nbsp;&nbsp;
<%= @exchange.province %>&nbsp;&nbsp;
<%= @exchange.city %>&nbsp;&nbsp;
<%= @exchange.region %>&nbsp;&nbsp;
<%= @exchange.address %>&nbsp;&nbsp;
<%= @exchange.zip %><br />
商品数量:<%= @exchange.count %><br />
